     ↓             ↓               ↓               ↓
TaskLauncher → ProgressTracker → ResultAggregator → AutoDocumenter
     ↓             ↓               ↓               ↓
Task Tool API → Real-time UI → PROTOCOL Parser → Session Store
```

### Componenti Chiave
- **Analysis Layer**: KeywordExtractor, DomainDetector, ComplexityAnalyzer
- **Routing Layer**: AgentRouter, ModelSelector, DependencyGraphBuilder
