## 🔗 Integration Points

### Task Tool Integration
```typescript
// Plugin wraps existing Task tool
TaskTool({
  subagent_type: mapToSubagentType(task.agentFile),
  instructions: `${agentContent}\n\nTASK: ${task.description}`,
  model: task.model,
  agent_id: task.id
});
```

### PROTOCOL.md Compliance
- **Mandatory response format** per tutti gli agent
- **Parsing automatico** di header, summary, files modified, etc.
- **Validation enforcement** per tutte le comunicazioni

### Agent File System
- **Read-only access** a `/agents/core/` e `/agents/experts/`
- **Dynamic parsing** di specializations e keywords
- **Zero modifiche** ai file agent esistenti

